Name:           Wind Element
Short Name:     wind
Level Required: 13

Description:
  The Wind Element is raw elemental Wind in living form. It attacks with
  a cyclone spell, blasting its foes with huge bursts of air.

Commands:
  - summon wind:    Summons it to you         (costs 80 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban wind:       Banishes it               (costs 30 sp)
